@lordof1000mimes: Night Exemplar huh? Will we be able to meet her inverse, Day Exemplar in a future set, perhaps?  

Sorry, had to do it. There's no excuse to misspell something like that when you can just look at the featured card's creature type for the correct spelling. >\_>  

Pet peeves aside, I favor her over [Hero of Oxid Ridge](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hero of Oxid Ridge), if primarily because she doesn't fall to a simple non-Metalcraft [Galvanic Blast](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Galvanic Blast). Great for any weenie/aggro deck.
